## 📄 API Endpoints

### Auth

* `POST /auth/register` → Create account
* `POST /auth/login` → Login and receive JWT

### Tasks (Requires JWT)

* `GET /tasks` → List all tasks
* `POST /tasks` → Add a new task
* `PUT /tasks/:id` → Update a task
* `DELETE /tasks/:id` → Delete a task

